Please edit this page to add your recommended R packages for all computers in biology:

# Dataframe 
1. dplyr
1. data.table
1. tidyr
1. chron


# Figures/Graphics
1. ggplot2
1. gridExtra


# Reproducible research
1. markdown
1. knitr
1. tinytex (install followed by `tinytex::install_tinytex()`)
1. kableExtra
1. magrittr


# Modeling 
1. bbmle
1. ade4
1. broom
1. deSolve
1. lme4

# Spatial data
1. sf
1. sp
1. rgdal (system dependencies: `GDAL`)
1. rgeos (system dependencies: `GEOS`)
1. raster
1. maps
1. mapview

# Etc
1. devtools
1. remotes
1. shiny
1. Rcpp


